latestPosts.caption:
Still feels like a dream 🧿

A silver play button has been on my vision board for the longest time and it always felt like a far fetched dream. We hit 100k on 11th Aug,2023 but the button arriving home was a completely different feeling and felt so unreal 🤍
7yrs of YouTube and this moment makes it all worth it! None of this would be possible without the love & support you cutus continue to shower upon me. Here's to making it to a million soon too 🫶🏻

Thank you @youtubeindia @youtubecreatorsindia @youtube for recognising my work, forever grateful 🥹

Unfiltered reaction video of my friends will be up tomorrow, dekhna okay guys?
